CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 15, 1959, pg. A2, reads: "Open Outhouse - An absentee landowner of this open lot in 1500 block of Colwell Street has not cleaned up the area which sloping land now stenches because it has been made into an open outhouse by some irresponsible citizens. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman standing on balcony of brick building pointing to lot full of debris used as "open outhouse," with laundry on railing and hanging in background, Colwell Street, Hill District
